00:01:45.176 --> 00:01:47.776 A:middle
Your iPad app should support

00:01:47.916 --> 00:01:50.166 A:middle
features like multitasking and

00:01:50.166 --> 00:01:52.726 A:middle
drag and drop as well as Auto

00:01:52.726 --> 00:01:53.076 A:middle
Layout.

00:01:54.506 --> 00:01:56.216 A:middle
As we all know, Mac windows can

00:01:56.216 --> 00:01:57.836 A:middle
be arbitrarily resized.

00:01:59.116 --> 00:02:00.676 A:middle
By fully supporting Auto Layout

00:01:59.116 --> 00:02:00.676 A:middle
By fully supporting Auto Layout

00:02:01.116 --> 00:02:03.716 A:middle
in your iPad app, your interface

