will be resizable on Mac.

00:02:07.476 --> 00:02:10.626 A:middle
Similarly, if your app supports

00:02:10.626 --> 00:02:12.556 A:middle
drag and drop, you're one step

00:02:12.626 --> 00:02:14.046 A:middle
closer to having a great Mac

00:02:14.046 --> 00:02:14.256 A:middle
app.

00:02:15.156 --> 00:02:16.916 A:middle
We expect just about everything

00:02:16.916 --> 00:02:19.056 A:middle
on Mac to be draggable and

00:02:19.056 --> 00:02:19.456 A:middle
droppable.

