00:20:26.426 --> 00:20:27.966 A:middle
They help differentiate your app

00:20:28.356 --> 00:20:30.516 A:middle
from dozens or hundreds of other

00:20:30.516 --> 00:20:31.716 A:middle
apps that people may have

00:20:31.716 --> 00:20:32.246 A:middle
