00:21:03.166 --> 00:21:05.016 A:middle
And I encourage you to do so.

00:21:05.816 --> 00:21:07.906 A:middle
Because of Mac app icon so much

00:21:07.906 --> 00:21:09.836 A:middle
more visible, it really pays to

00:21:09.836 --> 00:21:11.426 A:middle
have a great icon.

00:21:12.446 --> 00:21:14.256 A:middle
Mac icons have different design

00:21:14.256 --> 00:21:16.336 A:middle
characteristics than iOS icons.

00:21:17.056 --> 00:21:19.026 A:middle
They're not simply squares with

00:21:19.026 --> 00:21:20.156 A:middle
rounded off corners.

00:21:20.896 --> 00:21:22.866 A:middle
Mac app icons have unique

00:21:22.916 --> 00:21:25.116 A:middle
silhouettes to stand apart from

00:21:25.116 --> 00:21:26.256 A:middle
other app icons.

00:21:27.046 --> 00:21:28.806 A:middle
At smaller sizes, those

00:21:28.806 --> 00:21:30.716 A:middle
