00:21:30.796 --> 00:21:33.096 A:middle
easily distinguishable from each

00:21:33.096 --> 00:21:33.406 A:middle
other.

00:21:34.216 --> 00:21:37.106 A:middle
And, speaking of size, on a 1x

00:21:37.106 --> 00:21:39.266 A:middle
