00:21:39.266 --> 00:21:42.116 A:middle
are only 16 pixels tall by wide.

00:21:42.896 --> 00:21:44.586 A:middle
At this size, every pixel

00:21:44.586 --> 00:21:45.106 A:middle
counts.

00:21:45.646 --> 00:21:47.696 A:middle
So it's a good idea to create

00:21:47.696 --> 00:21:49.506 A:middle
pixel hinted icons at the

00:21:49.506 --> 00:21:51.296 A:middle
smallest app icon sizes.

00:21:52.866 --> 00:21:54.776 A:middle
Mac app icons are, of course,

00:21:55.156 --> 00:21:56.866 A:middle
crafted to accurately depict

00:21:57.306 --> 00:21:59.046 A:middle
physical real-world objects.

