Heavy keyboard users will thank

00:28:06.016 --> 00:28:08.816 A:middle
you on both Mac and iPad.

00:28:09.386 --> 00:28:11.036 A:middle
Your keyboard shortcuts will

00:28:11.036 --> 00:28:11.946 A:middle
work on both.

00:28:12.956 --> 00:28:14.446 A:middle
